A collection of externals from Iain Mott that mostly provide some matfunctions
for Pure Data:

polygate~ - switch between multiple signal inputs, variable fade rate both
linear & equal power

shuffle - a no-repeat random generator, outputs numbers within a set range

pan~ - equal power stereo panning

system - sends a system message to the console

ln~ - natural log + inverse

rec2pol~ - convert rectangular coordinates to polar eg. can be used to convert
sine & cosine rfft~ output to phase & magnitude

pol2rec~ - inverse of rec2pol~

getenv - Sends value of an environment variable argument on bang

WWW: http://puredata.info/downloads/motex
